  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Palm Simulator is a game in which you can become a palm tree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game will give you a meditative gameplay. You can stand and contemplate the beauty of the desert around you living your life as a palm tree. You can also perform actions that palm trees usually perform (stand in the same place). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a palm tree</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're in the desert</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are other palm trees around you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And not only palm trees</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 game mods: arcade and realistic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful stylized graphics</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Palm Simulator is a game in which you can become a palm tree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game will give you a meditative gameplay. You can stand and contemplate the beauty of the desert around you living your life as a palm tree. You can also perform actions that palm trees usually perform (stand in the same place). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a palm tree</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're in the desert</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are other palm trees around you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And not only palm trees</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 game mods: arcade and realistic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful stylized graphics</p></li></ul>",
